lead_paragraph: Joe Burns scored his third test century, while captain Steve Smith was in sight of his 14th at tea as Australia continued to chip away at New Zealand's first innings total on the second day of the second test on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Burns, Smith Frustrate New Zealand Bowlers
